          <h2>Content that speaks to AI and humans</h2>
          <p>The way people find information has fundamentally changed. ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overview are the new gatekeepers. We help you become the answer they deliver.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-card-inner">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
