                <h5>Answer Engine Optimization</h5>
                <p>Position your content to be the definitive answer when AI systems respond to user queries. Be the source that gets cited.</p>
              </div>
              <a href="/points-beyond/services/" class="feature-link">
                <span>Learn more</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="link-arrow">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.97 3.97a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l6.22-6.22H3a.75.75 0 010-1.5h16.19l-6.22-6.22a.75.75 0 010-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-card-inner">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-content">
                <h5>Search Engine Optimization</h5>
                <p>Proven techniques combined with AI-era strategies. Rank in both conventional results and AI-curated responses.</p>
              </div>
              <a href="/points-beyond/services/" class="feature-link">
                <span>Learn more</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="link-arrow">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.97 3.97a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l6.22-6.22H3a.75.75 0 010-1.5h16.19l-6.22-6.22a.75.75 0 010-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-card-inner">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-content">
                <h5>AI Voice Receptionist</h5>
                <p>Never miss a call. Our AI answers 24/7 with natural conversationâ€”booking appointments and answering FAQs.</p>
              </div>
              <a href="/points-beyond/services/" class="feature-link">
                <span>Learn more</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="link-arrow">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.97 3.97a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l6.22-6.22H3a.75.75 0 010-1.5h16.19l-6.22-6.22a.75.75 0 010-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card feature-highlight">
            <div class="feature-card-inner">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-content">
                <h5>Why Points Beyond?</h5>
                <p>Enterprise strategy experience applied to AI automation. We bridge proven transformation approaches with cutting-edge AI solutions.</p>
              </div>
              <a href="/points-beyond/about/" class="feature-link">
                <span>About us</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="link-arrow">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.97 3.97a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l6.22-6.22H3a.75.75 0 010-1.5h16.19l-6.22-6.22a.75.75 0 010-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section" id="contact">
      <div class="cta-gradient" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="gradient-blob gradient-left"></div>
        <div class="gradient-blob gradient-right"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Ready for the AI search era?</h2>
          <p>Get your free proposal and see how Points Beyond can position your business for success.</p>
          <div class="cta-form">
            <form action="#" method="POST">
              <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="url" name="website" placeholder="Website URL" />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
                <span>Get Your Free Proposal</span>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Urbanist:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

  .astrolus-page {
    --color-primary: #4f46e5;
    --color-primary-light: #818cf8;
    --color-secondary: #ea580c;
    --color-bg: #ffffff;
    --color-surface: #f9fafb;
    --color-text: #1f2937;
    --color-text-muted: #6b7280;
    --color-border: #e5e7eb;

    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: 'Urbanist', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding: 0 3rem;
    }
  }

  .text-primary {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        #ebe0ff 0%,
        #e0f2ff 40%,
        #ffffff 100%
      ) !important;
      padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
      min-height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .gradient-blob {
    filter: blur(106px);
  }

  .gradient-left {
    height: 14rem;
    /* Swapped vibrant indigo for a very pale lavender-grey */
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #eef2ff, #f5f3ff);
    margin-left: -13rem;
  }

  .gradient-right {
    height: 8rem;
    /* Swapped cyan for a very pale ice-blue */
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #f0f9ff, #e0f2fe);
    margin-top: 6rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    opacity: 1;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-text {
    max-width: 66.666%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #000000 !important;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero h1 .text-primary {
    color: #4f46e5 !important;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 2.75rem;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .btn-primary:active {
    transform: scale(0.95);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .btn-full {
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Hero Stats */
  .hero-stats {
    display: none;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
    }
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .stat-item h6 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .features-header {
    max-width: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-header {
      max-width: 66.666%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-header {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  .features-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .features-icon {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .features-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .features-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .feature-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    transition: z-index 0.1s, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .feature-card {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .feature-card:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .feature-card {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .feature-card:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .feature-card:last-child {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-highlight {
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .feature-highlight:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .feature-card-inner {
    position: relative;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .feature-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feature-content h5 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-content h5 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .feature-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .feature-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-link {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .link-arrow {
    width: 1.25rem;
    height: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-1rem);
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .link-arrow {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
      .cta-section {
        margin-top: 2rem; /* Reduced from 4rem to pull it closer to the cards */
        background: transparent;
        padding: 3rem 0 1rem; /* Tightened internal padding */
        text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    margin: auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    opacity: 0.4;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-content > p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-form {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .form-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .form-group input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'Urbanist', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .form-group input::placeholder {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .form-group input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-text {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .features {
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .cta-section {
    margin-top: 1.5rem; /* Nudged higher up from the cards */
    background: transparent;
    padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
